Terminal
The terminal component is a scrollable text console.
Text is appended as a stream. The component automatically manages:
• cursor position
• new lines
• word wrapping
• scrolling
• optional line numbers
Unlike lcd, text is not written at fixed coordinates. Characters are appended sequentially.
The terminal has a visual representation in the editor.

───

Syntax
text
comp [terminal] .name:
  rows: 20
  columns: 80
  fontSize: 12
  wordWrap: 1
  lineNumbers: 0
  :


