  append = ^426F6F74206F6B
  set = 1
}

.log:{
  newline = 1
  set = 1
}

.log:{
  append = ^435055207265616479
  set = 1
}

Display:
text
1 | Boot ok
2 | CPU ready


───

Inputs
append
Append one or more bytes.
text
append = value


───

newline
Move cursor to next line.
text
newline = 1


───

clear
Erase all contents.
text
clear = 1


───

set
Trigger execution.
text
set = expression

The block executes when the expression transitions from 0 to 1.

